      "acceptanceCriteria": "Ansys Mechanical 2022R2 used under controlled release with documented regression test suite; FDA-internal solver validated against NIST benchmarks.",
      "rationale": "All three FEA codes (FDA in-house, Ansys, DePuy Synthes commercial) operate under documented SQA plans. Regression testing covers the contact and nonlinear static solution paths used in this model. Version control and audit trails confirmed for all simulation runs. Achieved level exceeds required level for Medium model risk."
    },
    {
