      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed on the screw-rod assembly. Grid Convergence Index (GCI) for stiffness = 1.9%, yield force = 2.4%. Fine mesh (approx. 480k elements, hex-dominant in screw shank) adopted for all production runs. Discretization error assessed as adequately controlled."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical solver error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
