      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation scenario (F1717 static compression-bending) is the COU scenario; test articles are production-representative.",
      "rationale": "The validation activity is co-extensive with the COU: the FEA model is validated against the exact test standard (ASTM F1717) and device configuration (non-cannulated 7.5 mm screw, 5.5 mm rod, bilateral construct) that constitutes the regulatory submission basis. No extrapolation from a surrogate scenario is required. Relevance factor fully satisfied at required level."
